title: Stewart Rhodes -Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/20/19

description:
George Noory talks with Stewart Rhodes the founder of Oath Keepers about the effects of prescription drugs and how they can lead to depression and other mental illnesses.  They also touch on red flag laws and the El Paso mass shooting.
